    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1179.101388.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. The variation of measured characters in five European Cryphalus species. Pronotal lateral setae, mid (mm), refers to the length of the lateral setae on pronotum between the summit and the apex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/903286" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1179.101388.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Lateral and dorsal illustration of male genitalia of five European Cryphalus species." ;
